{"tid":2170336,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"印度擬收緊對中國簽證審查，限制中國機構在印活動","createTime":"2020-08-23T07:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T08:38:01.000Z","uid":48040,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dac9fca68029b0901ca808326c960cefcab625f4","tid":2170336,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"隨著兩國關係繼續惡化，印度正在加強對中國在印度相關活動的限制，包括增加對中國簽證的額外審查，並審查北京與當地大學的聯繫等。<br />\n<br />\n美國財經媒體彭博新聞社8月21日的報導引述不具名印度高級官員的話稱，印度外交部已被告知，<span class=\"orange\">中國商人、學者、業界專家和遊說團體的簽證將需要事先獲得安全許可。</span>印度官員說，這些措施與印度對巴基斯坦長期以來採取的措施類似。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/amp/india-new-curb-on-visas-schools-to-stem-china-influence/5553986.html?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=dlvr.it&amp;__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Famp%2Findia-new-curb-on-visas-schools-to-stem-china-influence%2F5553986.html%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Ddlvr.it%26__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTJdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=8181a6a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/amp/india-new-curb-on-visas-schools-to-stem-china-influence/5553986.html?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=dlvr.it&amp;__twitter_impression=true</a>"},{"pid":"9e3c4c668decaf88024ab9883de07b1f2e330042","tid":2170336,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:51:35.000Z","msg":"印度大學與中國相關機構的活動也可能會相應大幅縮減。印度政府目前正在審查印度理工學院(Indian Institutes Of Technology)、巴納拉斯印度教大學(Banaras Hindu University)、賈瓦哈拉爾&middot;尼赫魯大學(Jawaharlal Nehru University)等教育機構簽署的54份諒解備忘錄，這些機構與中國官方的中外語言交流合作中心，也就是人們所知的漢辦(Hanban)有聯繫，漢辦在世界各地經營孔子學院。<br />\n<br />\n印度官員說，除了普通話課程外，與中國機構的合作可能會中斷。他們說，這些機構被用來影響政策制定者、智庫、政黨、企業和學者。"},{"pid":"ffb4cc346df3cf1f484c97ff8c5d6d60ec6b91e9","tid":2170336,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:06:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a6f141b00de6455554cdb4bebd3e373fe0e41ee","tid":2170336,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffb4cc346df3cf1f484c97ff8c5d6d60ec6b91e9","tid":2170336,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:06:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"操你媽逼個叛國賊，咱們的煎餅果子不好吃麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c258d6bbc6ef686e79bd7f7bccb5c4b1591d5c","tid":2170336,"uid":270220,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:09:43.000Z","msg":"冇左膠阻頭阻勢真係效率一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7514c634381b56f4508983a3250b5903202575b","tid":2170336,"uid":189046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />印度好波"},{"pid":"b2b29d63e06c1331d1f52eb4282c7f6930a0a88c","tid":2170336,"uid":48040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"32c258d6bbc6ef686e79bd7f7bccb5c4b1591d5c","tid":2170336,"uid":270220,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:09:43.000Z","msg":"冇左膠阻頭阻勢真係效率一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:38:01.000Z","msg":"20名印度士兵生命喚醒國民"}]}